OL,3,CGreece general strike causes
OL,4,Cwidespread disruption across the
OL,5,Ccountry
OL,7,FA nationwide general strike in Greece
OL,8,Fhas caused widespread disruption to
OL,9,Fservices across the country, as public
OL,10,Fand private sector workers protest
OL,11,Fchanges to labour laws.
OL,13,FIt is the country's third general
OL,14,Fstrike this year.
OL,16,FThe 24-hour strike has disrupted
OL,17,Fpublic transport in Athens, with
OL,18,Fferries, taxis and trains halted.
