OL,7,FSchools, courts and public
OL,8,Fhospitalised are also facing
OL,9,Fdisruption.
OL,11,FTwo protest marches are planned in
OL,12,Fcentral Athens, with demonstrations
OL,13,Falso set for other cities.
OL,15,FUnions representing civil servants and
OL,16,Fprivate sector workers called the
OL,17,Fstrike to protest labour law changes
OL,18,Fthat will introduce more flexibility,
OL,19,Fincluding allowing overtime that could
OL,20,Fstretch shifts to 13 hours in a day.
