OL,7,FUnder the new regulations, working
OL,8,Fhours that include overtime would be
OL,9,Fcapped at 48 hours per week, with a
OL,10,Fmaximum 150 overtime hours allowed per
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FUnions argue the new rules leave
OL,14,Fworkers vulnerable to labour abuses by
OL,15,Femployers.
