OL,7,F"We say no to the 13-hour (shift).
OL,8,FExhaustion is not development, human
OL,9,Ftolerance has limits," the private
OL,10,Fsector umbrella union, the General
OL,11,FConfederation of Workers of Greece,
OL,12,Fsaid in a statement.
OL,14,FThe union called for a 37.5-hour
OL,15,Fworking week and the return of
OL,16,Fcollective bargaining agreements.
OL,18,FIn April, flights were grounded and
OL,19,Fpublic transport disrupted as workers
OL,20,Fwalked out in a general strike over
OL,21,Fwages.
